Superstar, Kizz Daniel has announced his 2022 world tour The singer said tour is tagged ‘Afroclassic world tour 2022’. The ‘Pour me water’ singer disclosed this recently on his verified Instagram page. The tour, he said, will see him sojourning various parts of Africa between January 2022 and March 2022.   AuGF, Nigeria minting company disagree over N162 billion…     Military neutralise three kidnappers in Jos     BREAKING: AMCON takes over IBEDC   He will continue on his musical tour in April 2022 to tour the UK and Ireland till May 2022. - Advertisement - June 2022 till August 2022 will see Kizz Daniel touring USA and Canada till September when he moves to Europe with his team till October 2022. The UAE and Middle East will have a taste of Kizz Daniel in November while he would return home in December 2022 to tour Nigeria. The tour, the singer said, would be under his new management One Africa Global Management led by Paul Okoye.